{"tid":2258571,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"行山旺季 2行山客暈倒 1死1昏迷　","createTime":"2020-10-26T06:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T13:16:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":120,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"f4447f1152db51f0fcd21ff684fc8a132c375d54","tid":2258571,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"秋高氣爽，正是郊遊好季節，然而行山人士亦要量力而為。今日兩小時內有兩宗行山人士遠足期間暈倒事件，一死一昏迷。早上8時許，一名姓于（74歲）老翁，到荃灣荃錦公路光板田村近芙蓉山行山期間，突暈倒地上，昏迷不醒，附近行山人士見狀，報警求助。救護員接報到場，將于伯送往仁濟醫院治理，其後被證實死亡。死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n至11時許，一名菲律賓女子在大嶼山昂坪棧道遠足期間，身體不適暈倒，政府飛行服務隊派出直升機到場，將她送往東區醫院救治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201026/INUZN77MHBGTDPNJ733Q224SIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201026%2FINUZN77MHBGTDPNJ733Q224SIU%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=679fb804\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201026%2FINUZN77MHBGTDPNJ733Q224SIU%2F&h=2c8e6c73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201026/INUZN77MHBGTDPNJ733Q224SIU/</a>"},{"pid":"33c8b6d0542088b3ed801d3317164a05bd796a2e","tid":2258571,"uid":128087,"like":204,"dislike":6,"score":198,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"搏盡無悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6617985d084ed49c1c6df5da52408aca7d3a3f11","tid":2258571,"uid":76804,"like":156,"dislike":11,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"今年行山死既多過武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3262932a344d023e0921d53935744825a0615963","tid":2258571,"uid":304916,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"33c8b6d0542088b3ed801d3317164a05bd796a2e","tid":2258571,"uid":128087,"like":204,"dislike":6,"score":198,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:47:37.000Z","msg":"搏盡無悔<img 