3fe3a73fb1598569c474cc11ee0ea6ff39","tid":2258571,"uid":4618,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6617985d084ed49c1c6df5da52408aca7d3a3f11","tid":2258571,"uid":76804,"like":156,"dislike":11,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"今年行山死既多過武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:01:23.000Z","msg":"其實點解今年會無啦啦有行山熱潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:30:18.000Z","msg":"近幾年都多左好多人行山喇<br />\n唔係今年既事<br />\n不過因為武肺真係多左啲人<br />\n但你感覺多左好多,主要因為多人批鬥姐<br />\n<br />\n媒體包括連登呢類討論區係好影響一個人價值觀<br />\n正如如果有鋁窗跌落黎整死人 咁新聞就日日報邊到跌鋁窗<br />\n有樹壓死人就日日講冧樹<br />\n有學童自殺就日日講幾多單跳樓<br />\n有工程醜聞果期就好似單單工程都有問題<br />\n個世界一直都係咁走 唔係突然間變潮流<br />\n係睇今期淪到邊個俾人擺上台姐"},{"pid":"16bbf258a4a85fc710b0660b2b14c188d276669b","tid":2258571,"uid":128974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4447f1152db51f0fcd21ff684fc8a132c375d54","tid":2258571,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:45:17.000Z","msg":"秋高氣爽，正是郊遊好季節，然而行山人士亦要量力而為。今日兩小時內有兩宗行山人士遠足期間暈倒事件，一死一昏迷。早上8時許，一名姓于（74歲）老翁，到荃灣荃錦公路光板田村近芙蓉山行山期間，突暈倒地上，昏迷不醒，附近行山人士見狀，報警求助。救護員接報到場，將于伯送往仁濟醫院治理，其後被證實死亡。死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n至11時許，一名菲律賓女子在大嶼山昂坪棧道遠足期間，身體不適暈倒，政府飛行服務隊派出直升機到場，將她送往東區醫院救治。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201026/INUZN77MHBGTDPNJ733Q224SIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201026%2FINUZN77MHBGTDPNJ733Q224SIU%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oG9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=679fb804\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201026%2FINUZN77MHBGTDPNJ733Q224SIU%2F&h=2c8e6c73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201026/INUZN77MHBGTDPNJ733Q224SIU/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:30:49.000Z","msg":"菲律賓人放假真係好鐘意行山"},{"pid":"9b92c52e642047afdc1553c94132e53f7878992c","tid":2258571,"uid":136226,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"52a63d3fe3a73fb1598569c474cc11ee0ea6ff39","tid":2258571,"uid":4618,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"6617985d084ed49c1c6df5da52408aca7d3a3f11","tid":2258571,"uid":76804,"like":156,"dislike":11,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T06:48:39.000Z","msg":"今年行山死既多過武肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:01:23.000Z","msg":"其實點解今年會無啦啦有行山熱潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"年年都係呢個時候架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44767e1802be6c8d1e14433926f5fbb4f4196e8d","tid":2258571,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:39:57.000Z","msg":"612就黎冇錢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2257791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2257791</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}